===Etymology===
Coined by [[singer]] [[w:Justin_Timberlake|Justin Timberlake]] to explain [[w:Super Bowl XXXVIII Halftime show controversy|incident during the Super Bowl]] in which [[w:Janet_Jackson|Janet Jackson]]'s right [[breast]] was unintentionally bared.

===Noun phrase===
'''[[wardrobe]] [[malfunction]]''' (''plural'' '''wardrobe malfunctions''')

#(''[[euphemistic]]'') An accidental instance of [[indecent exposure]] caused by a fault in someone's [[clothing]] (especially that of a performer) or by an error made while changing this costume.

